<div class="App">
  <div class="container">
    {{> jumbotron}}
      {{#if flashMessages }}
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12">
          {{#if flashMessages.success }}
            <div id="success" class="alert alert-success">
              {{flashMessages.success}}
            </div>
          {{else if flashMessages.error }}
            <div id="error" class="alert alert-warning">
              {{flashMessages.error}}
            </div>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      {{/if}}
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h1 class="mt-5">
              MongoDB is part of the GitHub Student Developer Pack
            </h1>
            <p class="lead">
              Learn more about the
              <a href="https://education.github.com/pack">
                GitHub Student Developer Pack
              </a>
            </p>
            <p>
              MongoDB is a general purpose, document-based, distributed
              database built for modern application developers and for the
              cloud era. No database makes you more productive.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">

            <h2 class="mt-5">
              Benefits of Participation
              </h1>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
            <Image width="100" src="/images/compass.png" fluid thumbnail></Image>
            <div class="benefitHeader">MongoDB Compass</div>
            <div class="benefit text-left">
              MongoDB Compass is the GUI for MongoDB. Compass allows you to
              analyze and understand the contents of your data without
              formal knowledge of MongoDB query syntax. In addition to
              exploring your data in a visual environment, you can also use
              Compass to optimize query performance, manage indexes, and
              implement document validation.
            </div>
            <br></br>
            <a class="btn btn-dark btn-sm" href="https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/compass" role='button'>
              Learn More
            </a>
            
        

          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
            <Image width="100" src="/images/student.png" fluid thumbnail></Image>
            <div class="benefitHeader">
              MongoDB University On-Demand
            </div>
            <div class="benefit text-left">
              All of our MongoDB University training courses - from beginner
              to advanced - are completely free for anyone and everyone. As
              part of the on-demand program you are able to take the courses
              at your leisure rather than having to adhere to our normal
              course schedule.
            </div>
            <br></br>
            <a role="button" href="https://university.mongodb.com/" class='btn btn-dark btn-sm' variant="dark" size="sm">
              Learn More
            </a>
            
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
            <Image width="100" src="/images/cloud.png" fluid thumbnail></Image>
            <div class="benefitHeader">
              $200 in MongoDB Atlas Credits
            </div>
            <div class="benefit text-left">
              MongoDB Atlas is the global cloud database service for
              applications built on MongoDB. You can easily deploy fully
              managed databases within minutes to get started. If you scale
              up, MongoDB Atlasâ€™ automation and proven best practices
              guarantee availability, scalability, and compliance with the
              most demanding data security and privacy standards.
            </div>
            <br></br>
            <a role="button" href="https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas" class='btn btn-dark btn-sm' variant="dark"
              size="sm">
              Learn More
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center signup">
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              {{#if user}}
                {{#if user.isStudent}}
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <h4>Welcome {{user.name}}</h4>
                <hr>
                <p>
                  Visit your <a href="/profile">profile</a> to view your benefit codes and links to products and
                  downloads.
                </p>
              </div>

                {{else}}
              <p>
                Welcome and thanks for logging in. Unfortunately, we are unable to verify your status as a participant
                in the GitHub Student Developer Pack. Please visit <a href=https://education.github.com/benefits> the
                  GitHub Student Pack home</a> for additional information and to register. </p> 
                  
                {{/if}} 
              {{else}} 
                <a class="btn btn-warning" href="https://github.com/login/oauth/authorize?client_id={{client_id}}"
                  role="button">Sign in with GitHub</a>
              {{/if}}

            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
{{> faq}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>